column22: All the class room in the school have been occupied. Only the office of the head teacher and the Laboratory is left.
There are two villages camping in this facility, Bulla Kamor   A&B  and 	Bulla Vumbi
They have occupied all the classes, 4hhs in each class.; The camps chairman is Yussuf Ahmed of tel. no: 0721547298; 8 toilets open for the IDPs.

column20: Totally cut off from the rest of the county
